text.tspan: We are 95% confident that the probability of ordering from Pizza Hut changes
by between a reduction of 10.3% to an increase of 31.7% when the price drops.
Students at Miami University were surveyed to evaluate how price affected whether
a pizza was ordered from Pizza Hut or another pizzeria. Of the students, 28 were
told the regular Pizza Hut price and 35 were given a reduced price.
